ts\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4801}, {\"ngram\": \"100 milliliters\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not a \\\"magic\\\" number though, Iovine said, and officials likely take into account additional factors - like the weather - when making decisions about the water quality.\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 5007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4869, \"end\": 4875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Iovine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.6242550185052806e-21, \"text\": \"Iovine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Iovine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Iovine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"magic\\\" number\", \"from\": 4844, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"account\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4920}, {\"ngram\": \"additional factors\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 4958}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 4973, \"to\": 4982}, {\"ngram\": \"the water quality\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 5006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a sunny day, the sun's ultraviolet rays can kill the bacteria and lower levels.\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sunny day\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5023}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun's ultraviolet rays\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5051}, {\"ngram\": \"the bacteria\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"lower levels\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happens when you swim in contaminated water?\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contaminated water\", \"from\": 5123, \"to\": 5141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimming in water with unsafe levels of bacteria can lead to an upset stomach and intestinal problems.\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5161}, {\"ngram\": \"unsafe levels\", \"from\": 5167, \"to\": 5180}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5192}, {\"ngram\": \"an upset stomach\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5221}, {\"ngram\": \"intestinal problems\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmers may inadvertently swallow the water or pick up infections through open cuts.\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swimmers\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5255}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5291}, {\"ngram\": \"infections\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5313}, {\"ngram\": \"open cuts\", \"from\": 5322, \"to\": 5331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even a mouthful of contaminated water can lead to diarrhea, and germs can cause illnesses such as infections in the urinary tract or in the intestines, or in the worst-case scenario, life-threatening sepsis.\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contaminated water\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5371}, {\"ngram\": \"diarrhea\", \"from\": 5384, \"to\": 5392}, {\"ngram\": \"germs\", \"from\": 5398, \"to\": 5403}, {\"ngram\": \"illnesses\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"infections\", \"from\": 5432, \"to\": 5442}, {\"ngram\": \"the urinary tract\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"the intestines\", \"from\": 5470, \"to\": 5484}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst-case scenario, life-threatening sepsis\", \"from\": 5492, \"to\": 5540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athletes are young, and they are in the best shape of anybody, so they are gonna be more resilient than many of us,\\\" Iovine said.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 5544, \"to\": 5556}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shape\", \"from\": 5584, \"to\": 5598}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5609}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5662}, {\"ngram\": \"Iovine\", \"from\": 5665, \"t